OL,4,Cyear-old son accepts she let him down
OL,6,FA mother whose parents are accused of
OL,7,Fmurdering her son accepts she should
OL,8,Fhave done more for him and she let him
OL,9,Fdown.
OL,11,FUnder cross-examination at Mold Crown
OL,12,FCourt, Shannon Ives was asked by
OL,13,Fprosecuting barrister Caroline Rees
OL,14,FKC: "Do you accept in your way that
OL,15,Fyou neglected Ethan too?"
OL,17,F"Yes," she answered.
