OL,3,CMum accused of allowing death of two-
OL,4,Cyear-old son accepts she let him down
OL,6,FMichael Ives, 47, and Kerry Ives, 46,
OL,7,Fdeny murdering Ethan Ives Griffiths.
OL,8,FThey along with their daughter Shannon
OL,9,FIves, 28, also deny causing or
OL,10,Fallowing his death and child cruelty.
OL,12,FThe two-year-old collapsed whilst in
OL,13,Fthe care of his grandparents on 14th
OL,14,FAugust 2021. It is the prosecution's
OL,15,Fcase that he was shaken or hit,
OL,16,Fcausing a catastrophic brain injury.
OL,18,FHe died two days later at Alder Hey
OL,19,FHospital in Liverpool .
