OL,3,CMum accused of allowing death of two-
OL,4,Cyear-old son accepts she let him down
OL,6,FShannon Ives told the court she should
OL,7,Fhave spoken to a health visitor or
OL,8,Fsocial worker and should have got
OL,9,Fmedical attention for Ethan.
OL,11,FShe also admitted she should have
OL,12,Fphoned police when she saw Michael
OL,13,FIves carrying her son by his arm or
OL,14,F"shaking Ethan".
OL,16,FHowever, alluding to her parents she
OL,17,Fsaid: "Them two were controlling me".
