OL,3,CMum accused of allowing death of two-
OL,4,Cyear-old son accepts she let him down
OL,6,FShe said her parents made her lie to
OL,7,Fsocial services and say Kerry Ives had
OL,8,FCovid when she did not. This action
OL,9,Fprevented people from coming into
OL,10,Ftheir home in Garden City, Flintshire,
OL,11,Fand checking on Ethan.
OL,13,FCaroline Rees KC said: "You didn't do
OL,14,Fwhat a Mum should do?"
OL,16,FMs Ives, who cried throughout the
OL,17,Fcross-examination, responded: "No."
OL,19,FMs Rees added: "You should've done a
OL,20,Flot more for Ethan."
